<body>
    <div class="container-noti">
        <div class="header-noti">
            <div class="logo-noti">
               <img src="{{client_logo()}}" alt="{{donor.donor_name or '--'}} mGrant Logo">
            </div>
            <h1 style="color: #333; margin-top: 15px;">Fund Request Reminder - 14 Days</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content-noti">
            <h2 style="color: #8B1818;">Dear {{ngo.ngo_name or 'Partner'}},</h2>

            <p>This is an urgent reminder to raise fund request for <strong>{{doc.grant}}</strong> Tranche <strong>{{doc.name}}</strong>. The tranche is scheduled for disbursement in 14 days on {{ frappe.utils.format_date(doc.planned_due_date, "dd-MM-yyyy") }}.</p>

            <div class="urgent-reminder-box">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">⏰ Urgent - Tranche Information</h4>
                <p><strong>Grant ID:</strong> {{doc.grant}}</p>
                <p><strong>Grantee:</strong> {{ngo.ngo_name}}</p>
                <p><strong>Tranche Number:</strong> {{doc.name}}</p>
                <p><strong>Scheduled Disbursement:</strong> {{ frappe.utils.format_date(doc.planned_due_date, "dd-MM-yyyy") }}</p>
                <p><strong>Days Until Disbursement:</strong> 14 days</p>
                <p><strong>Tranche Amount:</strong> ₹ {{format_currency(doc.total_funds_planned)}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="action-box">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #117a8b;">Action Required - Submit Fund Request</h4>
                <p><strong>To ensure timely disbursement:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Complete and submit quarterly reports immediately</li>
                    <li>Update utilization details on the portal</li>
                    <li>Enter interest earned on received funds</li>
                    <li>Submit fund request through mGrant portal</li>
                    <li>Allow time for approval and processing</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p><a href="/app/grant/{{doc.grant}}#tranche_tab" class="button-noti">Submit Fund Request</a></p>

            <p><strong>Time-sensitive:</strong> Please complete your quarterly reporting and submit your fund request immediately through the mGrant portal to ensure disbursement is processed on time.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br>The {{donor.donor_name}} Grants Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-noti">
            <p>© {{ frappe.utils.getdate().year }} {{donor.donor_name}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>For support, contact: <a href="mailto:{{mg.support_email or 'support@mgrant.org'}}">{{mg.support_email or 'support@mgrant.org'}}</a></p>
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

