<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>

    <meta charset="utf-8">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>{{donor.donor_name}} mGrant - MoU Signing Ongoing</title>

    <style>

        body {

            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;

            line-height: 1.6;

            margin: 0;

            padding: 0;

            background-color: #f5f5f5;

            color: #333;

        }

        .container-noti {

            max-width: 600px;

            margin: 0 auto;

            padding: 20px;

            background-color: white;

            border-radius: 12px;

            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);

        }

        .header-noti {

            text-align: center;

            padding: 25px 0;

            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;

            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8f9fa, #fff);

            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;

        }

        .logo-noti {

            width: 100px;

            height: 100px;

            margin: 0 auto 15px;

        }

        .logo-noti img {

            width: 100%;

            height: 100%;

            object-fit: contain;

        }

        .content-noti {

            padding: 30px 25px;

        }

        .section-noti {

            margin: 25px 0;

            padding: 20px;

            background-color: #f8f9fa;

            border-radius: 8px;

            border-left: 4px solid #8B1818;

        }

        .section-title {

            color: #8B1818;

            font-weight: 600;

            margin-bottom: 15px;

            font-size: 1.1em;

        }

        .button-noti {

            display: inline-block;

            padding: 14px 28px;

            background-color: #8B1818;

            color: white;

            text-decoration: none;

            border-radius: 8px;

            margin: 20px 0;

            text-align: center;

            font-weight: 500;

            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;

        }

       .details-grid p {

            margin: 0px !important;

        }

        .details-label {

            color: #666;

            font-weight: 500;

        }

        .details-value {

            color: #333;

            font-weight: 500;

        }

        .footer-noti {

            text-align: center;

            padding: 25px;

            color: #666;

            font-size: 14px;

            border-top: 1px solid #eee;

            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8f9fa, #fff);

            border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;

        }

    </style>

</head>

<body>

    <div class="container-noti">

        <div class="header-noti">

            <div class="logo-noti">

               <img src="{{client_logo()}}" alt="{{donor.donor_name or '--'}} mGrant Logo">

            </div>

            <h1 style="color: #333; margin: 15px 0 5px;">MoU Signing Ongoing</h1>

        </div>



        <div class="content-noti">

            <h2 style="color: #8B1818; margin-bottom: 25px;">Dear {{rfp.spoc_name}},</h2>



            <p>The application submitted against the RFP has progressed to the MoU Signing Ongoing stage.</p>



            <div class="section-noti">

                <div class="section-title">Application Details</div>

                <div class="details-grid">
                    <p><span class="details-label">RFP Title:</span> 
                       <span class="details-value">{{ rfp.title }}</span></p>

                    <p><span class="details-label">NGO:</span> 
                       <span class="details-value">{{ doc.ngo_name }}</span></p>

                    <!--
                    <p><span class="details-label">Submission Date:</span> 
                       <span class="details-value">{{ frappe.utils.format_date(frappe.utils.today(), "dd-MM-yyyy") }}</span></p>
                    -->

                    <p><span class="details-label">Current Stage:</span> 
                       <span class="details-value">MoU Signing Ongoing</span></p>
                </div>

            </div>



            <div class="section-noti">

                <div class="section-title">Next Steps</div>

                <p>Please follow these steps:</p>

                <ol>

                    <li>Review the attached draft MoU carefully. If any changes are required, edit the application details and re-generate MoU</li>

                    <li>Once you have reviewed the MoU, ensure L1, L2, and L3 approvers review and provide their approvals</li>

                    <li>Once approvals are received, proceed to get the MoU signed offline with all parties</li>

                    <li>Upload the final signed MoU in the application's Final MoU section and change the application stage to "MoU Signed"</li>

                </ol>

            </div>


            {% if doc.level_1_users or doc.level_2_users or doc.level_3_users %}
            <div class="section">

                <div class="section-title">Approver Details</div>

                <div class="details-grid">
                    {% if doc.level_1_users%}
                    <div style="display: flex;margin-left:2px;flex-direction: row;">
                        <span class="details-label">L1 Approver:</span>
                        {% for user in doc.level_1_users %}
                            <div style="display: flex;margin-left:6px;flex-direction: column;">
                                <p class="details-value">{{user.user_name}} ({{user.user_email}})</p>
                                <p class="details-value">{{user.user_name}} ({{user.user_email}})</p>
                                <p class="details-value">{{user.user_name}} ({{user.user_email}})</p>
                            </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}


                    {% if doc.level_2_users%}
                        <div style="display: flex;margin-left:2px;flex-direction: row;">
                            <span class="details-label">L2 Approver:</span>
                            {% for user in doc.level_2_users %}
                                <div style="display: flex;margin-left:6px;flex-direction: column;">
                                    <p class="details-value">{{user.user_name}} ({{user.user_email}})</p>
                                </div>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}



                    {% if doc.level_3_users%}
                        <div style="display: flex;margin-left:2px;flex-direction: row;">
                            <span class="details-label">L3 Approver:</span>
                            {% for user in doc.level_3_users %}
                                <div style="display: flex;margin-left:6px;flex-direction: column;">
                                    <p class="details-value">{{user.user_name}} ({{user.user_email}})</p>
                                </div>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                </div>

            </div>
            {% endif %}



            <center><a href="/app/proposal/{{doc.name}}" class="button-noti">Go to Application</a></center>



            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Best regards,<br>The {{donor.donor_name}} mGrant Team</p>

        </div>



        <div class="footer-noti">

           <p>© {{ frappe.utils.getdate().year }} {{donor.donor_name}}. All rights reserved.</p>

        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>

